title: Final Critical Habitat for the Leopard darter (Percina pantherina)
name: final-critical-habitat-for-the-leopard-darter-percina-pantherina01197
notes: To provide the user with a general idea of areas where final critical habitat for Leopard darter (Percina pantherina) occur based on the description provided in the Federal Register. The geographic extent includes McCurtain and Pushmataha Counties, Oklahoma ; Polk County, Arkansas.
